dc_title_s: Map of the Hindu Kush and the regions adjoining, to illustrate the journey of Benedict Goës compiled by H. Y.
dc_description_s: Shows "route of Goës." Relief shown by hachures. Lithographer Edward Weller. "Names used by Goës." Gives "obsolete names." Map "To face title of part II" of ["Cathay and the way thither ... by Henry Yule, c.b."]. 1 map: col.; 32 x 50 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
